{"tid":2212256,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「香港自秦朝已為中國領土」 齡記初中歷史書《基本法》夾硬與古巴比倫苛法掛鈎","createTime":"2020-09-21T15:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T05:43:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"36f37ebfdeb1c224a0b11ac0402b94ad944e054d","tid":2212256,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:55:44.000Z","msg":"教育局大幅「河蟹」高中通識科教科書有關六四事件、公民抗命等內容後，有今年出版的初中歷史科教科書，將古代歷史與《基本法》掛鈎。在關於約3,700多年前古巴比倫王國制定律法的內容，加插《基本法》指香港居民在法律面前一律平等；又指香港被秦朝劃入版圖，因此《基本法》列明香港特區是中國不可分離的部份。有歷史科老師質疑出版社為了滿足教育局，才加入有關內容。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/USLLBU4ELBB77JZTOHWER3PVXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2FUSLLBU4ELBB77JZTOHWER3PVXE%2F&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zERkIbV9%2FoY%2BmeTBoP0X2IjM%3D&h=2eb670ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2FUSLLBU4ELBB77JZTOHWER3PVXE%2F&h=9bf42bee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/USLLBU4ELBB77JZTOHWER3PVXE/</a>"},{"pid":"e65206c534014d984cdb4dd2021cccabd7a7d662","tid":2212256,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T15:56:56.000Z","msg":"please help me do that task<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTwitter新戰線: #StopHKCensorship<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2212252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2212252</a>"},{"pid":"4b5b4896960c397c1ce8666f1cb0ed56caa63911","tid":2212256,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class